    <title>Frontiers | Made-to-order spiking neuron model equipped with a multi-timescale adaptive threshold | Frontiers in Computational Neuroscience</title>

    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="http://e01f3a53c0bf5cbade8a-d4a9ca15fc46ba40e71f94dec0aad28c.r40.cf1.rackcdn.com/favicon_16x16.ico" type="image/x-icon" />

