</div></div>
<div class="fulltextdescription"><div><a name="B62" id="B62"></a>

Yang, C. R., Seamans, J. K., and Gorelova, N. (1996). Electrophysiological and morphological properties of layers V-VI principal pyramidal cells in rat prefrontal cortex in vitro. <i>J. Neurosci.</i> 16, 1904&#x02013;1921.
</div><div class="referenceslink"><a href="http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/sites/entrez?Db=pubmed&#x00026;Cmd=ShowDetailView&#x00026;TermToSearch=8774458" target="_blank">Pubmed Abstract</a>

 | <a href="http://eutils.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?db=pubmed&#x00026;cmd=prlinks&#x00026;retmode=ref&#x00026;id=8774458" target="_blank">Pubmed Full Text</a>

</div></div>
